    <div class="main">
      <div class="card"><div class="card-title">What is Omnisend?</div><div class="prose"><p>Omnisend is an email and SMS marketing platform built specifically for ecommerce — it's the most popular Klaviyo alternative, offering similar ecommerce-focused features at a significantly lower price point. Used by 100,000+ ecommerce brands including those on Shopify, WooCommerce and BigCommerce.</p><p>Its pre-built automation workflows cover all the key ecommerce scenarios — abandoned cart, welcome series, post-purchase, browse abandonment, win-back and cross-sell — and can be activated in minutes without custom configuration. Unlike Mailchimp, every automation is built with ecommerce revenue in mind.</p><p>Omnisend's channel mixing is a standout feature — you can combine email, SMS and web push notifications in the same automation workflow, reaching customers on whichever channel they're most responsive to. Its free plan is generous and the paid plans are typically 30-50% cheaper than equivalent Klaviyo plans.</p></div></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-title">Key Features</div><div class="features-grid"><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">🛒</div><div class="feat-name">Ecommerce Automations</div><div class="feat-desc">Pre-built abandoned cart, welcome, post-purchase and win-back workflows — activate in minutes, not hours.</div></div><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">📱</div><div class="feat-name">Email + SMS + Push</div><div class="feat-desc">Combine email, SMS and web push in one automation workflow — reach customers on their preferred channel.</div></div><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">🎯</div><div class="feat-name">Segmentation</div><div class="feat-desc">Segment by purchase history, browsing behaviour, engagement and 50+ ecommerce-specific data points.</div></div><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">🤖</div><div class="feat-name">AI Content Tools</div><div class="feat-desc">AI-generated subject lines, send time optimisation and product recommendations personalised per subscriber.</div></div><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">📊</div><div class="feat-name">Revenue Reporting</div><div class="feat-desc">Direct revenue attribution per campaign, flow and channel — see exactly what each email and SMS earns.</div></div><div class="feat-item"><div class="feat-icon">🔗</div><div class="feat-name">Shopify Integration</div><div class="feat-desc">Deep native Shopify sync — products, orders and customer data updated in real time.</div></div></div></div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">Pros & Cons</div>
        <div class="pros-cons">
          <div class="pros"><div class="pc-title">What we love</div><div class="pc-item">30-50% cheaper than Klaviyo for same features</div><div class="pc-item">Email + SMS + push in one platform</div><div class="pc-item">Excellent pre-built ecommerce automations</div><div class="pc-item">Generous free plan</div><div class="pc-item">Easy setup — pre-built workflows ready to go</div></div>
          <div class="cons"><div class="pc-title">Watch out for</div><div class="pc-item">Less powerful segmentation than Klaviyo</div><div class="pc-item">Smaller integration library</div><div class="pc-item">Predictive analytics less advanced than Klaviyo</div><div class="pc-item">Smaller community and ecosystem</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-title">Frequently Asked Questions</div><div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Is Omnisend better than Klaviyo? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">For most small and mid-size ecommerce brands, Omnisend delivers 80-90% of Klaviyo's functionality at a lower price — making it the better value choice. Klaviyo edges ahead for advanced segmentation, predictive analytics and brands that need maximum customisation. If you're spending over $50K/month on email marketing or have a large, complex list, Klaviyo's power justifies the premium. For most stores, Omnisend is excellent.</div></div><div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Does Omnisend have a free plan? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">Yes — Omnisend's free plan supports up to 250 contacts and 500 emails/month, plus up to 60 SMS credits. It includes pre-built automations, templates and basic segmentation. The free plan is enough to set up abandoned cart and welcome flows before upgrading. Paid plans start at $16/month.</div></div><div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Does Omnisend work with Shopify? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a">Yes — Omnisend has a deep native Shopify integration that syncs all customer, order and product data in real time. It's one of the top-rated email apps in the Shopify App Store. The integration enables product recommendation blocks, purchase-triggered automations and revenue attribution tracking automatically once connected.</div></div></div>
